## Task: Add human (user) safety-rule authoring to the Osprey Policy UI

**Run after A.5-UI-R (it discovered the Policy UI stack).** Today, Osprey rules are written by **Sara**
(the agent) via `saveRule`/`validateRules`. This adds a **human-facing rule-authoring experience** so an
operator/rule-author can create, validate, preview, and deploy Osprey safety rules themselves — reusing
the existing engine, not reimplementing it. Additive only.

